snippet.title: Team Sonic Racing Overdrive: Part 2
snippet.description:
It's Team Dark VS. Team Sonic as the race heats up! From trickery to teamwork, each team is trying their hardest to take the top spot. With the finish line in sight, only one team can take home the victory! 

Team Sonic Racing arrives May 21st for Playstation 4, Xbox One, Nintendo Switch, and PC!

Pre-Order now: https://bit.ly/2IFbIOz

Special thanks to everyone who worked so hard on Team Sonic Racing: Overdrive, including Tyson Hesse, Neko Productions, Ian Mutchler, Sonic Team, and Jun Senoue!
